Subject: [ghostium] AnalyserNode readback noise hook

Spec-D wiring. Anchors at top of ``analyser_node.cc``. The real calls
into ``FingerprintNoiseSource::ApplyAudioNoise`` (float-domain) and
``ApplyAudioByteNoise`` (uint8 domain) land inside the four readback
paths:
  * ``getFloatFrequencyData`` (float dB magnitudes)
  * ``getByteFrequencyData`` (uint8 quantised magnitudes)
  * ``getFloatTimeDomainData`` (float PCM)
  * ``getByteTimeDomainData`` (uint8 quantised PCM)

All four are deterministic per the profile's ``audio_seed``.

---
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webaudio/analyser_node.cc | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webaudio/analyser_node.cc b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webaudio/analyser_node.cc
--- a/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webaudio/analyser_node.cc
+++ b/third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webaudio/analyser_node.cc
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
